<bioghist encodinganalog="545"><head>History of Xavier University Department of Education</head><p>In 2006 the Xavier University Department of Education became the School of Education which encompassed different departments. As of May, 2015 the departments represented in the School of Education are: the Department of Secondary and Special Education, the Department of Educational Leadership and Human Resource Development, and the Department of Childhood Education and Literacy. The Department of School and Community Counseling which at one time was part of the School of Education later became the Department of Counseling (apart from the School of Education) in the College of Social Sciences, Health, and Education.</p><bioghist/></bioghist><scopecontent encodinganalog="520$a"><head>Scope and Content</head><p>Documents in this collection include meeting minutes, correspondence, reports and proposals.</p><scopecontent/></scopecontent><arrangement encodinganalog="351$b"><head>Statement of Arrangement</head><p>Materials are arranged into the following series:</p><list type="simple"><item>Meeting Minutes, Correspondence, and Reports</item><item>Montessori Education Program</item><item>Brochures, Pamphlets, and Other Publications</item><item>State of Ohio Reports and Evaluations</item><item>Proposal for Doctor of Education Program</item></list></arrangement><relatedmaterial encodinganalog="544 1"><head>Related Material</head><p>Materials received from the current Xavier University School of Education will be held separately under that school's records.</p></relatedmaterial><accessrestrict encodinganalog="506"><head>Restrictions on Access</head><p>Some materials may have restricted access. Please contact the archives staff.</p></accessrestrict><prefercite encodinganalog="524"><head>Preferred Citation</head><p>Box Number, Folder Number, XUA-77, Xavier University Department of Education records, Special Collections and Archives, Xavier University, Cincinnati, Ohio.</p></preferc